---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import localPackGoogle from '../../../assets/local-pack-google.png'
---

<section class='relative overflow-hidden bg-petrol-50 py-24 sm:py-32'>

  <!-- Dot-grid texture -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,60,74,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;'
  ></div>

  <!-- Ghost watermark -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none leading-none'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive; font-size: clamp(12rem, 24vw, 20rem); color: rgba(249,115,22,0.04); line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap;'
  >
    WEB
  </div>

  <!-- Radial ambient glow -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14,165,233,0.04) 0%, transparent 65%);'
  ></div>

  <!-- Top/bottom hairlines -->
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-petrol-100 to-transparent' aria-hidden='true'></div>
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-petrol-100 to-transparent' aria-hidden='true'></div>

  <div class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8'>
    <div class='mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_480px] lg:gap-16 xl:gap-24 items-center'>

      <!-- LEFT: Plain explanation -->
      <div>

        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <div data-animate class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-8'>
          <span class='block h-px w-10 bg-orange-500' aria-hidden='true'></span>
          <p class='label-section text-orange-500'>
            En palabras simples
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Titan One display — visual only, not semantic heading -->
        <p
          data-animate
          style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'
          class='leading-[0.92] tracking-tight mb-6'
        >
          <span class='block text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3rem)] text-petrol-700'>
            Que te encuentren a ti
          </span>
          <span class='block text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5rem)] text-petrol-900'>
            antes que a ellos<span class='text-orange-400'>.</span>
          </span>
        </p>

        <!-- Orange accent rule -->
        <div data-animate class='flex items-center mb-8' aria-hidden='true'>
          <div class='h-[3px] w-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-full'></div>
          <div class='h-px w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/40 to-transparent'></div>
        </div>

        <p data-animate class='text-base/8 text-body text-pretty'>
          Cuando alguien necesita un fontanero, un abogado o un dentista en Barcelona, abre Google y escribe lo que busca. En menos de un segundo, Google le muestra una lista de negocios.
        </p>

        <p data-animate class='mt-4 text-base/8 text-body text-pretty'>
          <strong class='text-heading font-semibold'>El 91% del tráfico orgánico se queda en la primera página de Google.</strong> Los de la segunda, prácticamente ninguno.
        </p>

        <p data-animate class='mt-4 text-base/8 text-body text-pretty'>
          Posicionamiento web es el trabajo que hace que Google muestre tu negocio antes que el de tu competencia.
        </p>

        <!-- Stat pills -->
        <div data-animate class='mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3'>
          <div class='stat-pill'>
            <span class='stat-num'>91%</span>
            <span class='stat-label'>del tráfico orgánico se queda en pág. 1</span>
          </div>
          <div class='stat-pill'>
            <span class='stat-num'>0 €</span>
            <span class='stat-label'>por clic, a diferencia de los anuncios</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: Google Local Pack screenshot -->
      <div data-animate class='mt-12 lg:mt-0'>
        <div class='serp-wrapper'>
          <Image
            src={localPackGoogle}
            alt='Resultados de Google para "fontanero urgente barcelona" mostrando el Local Pack con empresas en el mapa'
            width={530}
            height={700}
            class='w-full h-auto block'
            loading='lazy'
          />
        </div>
        <p class='mt-3 text-center text-xs text-petrol-600/60'>Captura real de Google · Local Pack para "fontanero urgente barcelona"</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ── Stat pills ── */
  .stat-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.1rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(26,60,74,0.06);
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Titan One', cursive;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-petrol-900);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-petrol-600);
    line-height: 1.3;
    max-width: 12ch;
  }

  /* ── SERP wrapper ── */
  .serp-wrapper {
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26,60,74,0.08), 0 1px 3px rgba(26,60,74,0.06);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: white;
  }
</style>
